## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-197">Una ricerca asincrona può visualizzare i risultati quando vengono individuate durante la ricerca simultaneamente altri risultati.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-197">An asynchronous search can show results as they are found while simultaneously searching for additional results.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-198">Ciò è utile per le attività come il popolamento di caselle di riepilogo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-198">This is useful for tasks such as populating list boxes.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-199">L'impostazione predefinita di questa proprietà è `false`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-199">The default setting for this property is `false`.</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-200">Nell'esempio c# seguente viene illustrato come creare una ricerca asincrona.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-200">The following C# example shows how to create an asynchronous search.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
//Set the Asynchronous property to true.  
src.Asynchronous = true;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-204">L'attributo che questa proprietà è impostata su deve essere un attributo di nome distinto, ad esempio managedBy o membro.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-204">The attribute that this property is set to must be a distinguished name attribute, such as member or managedBy.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-205">L'attributo può essere singolo o multivalore.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-205">The attribute can be either single or multi-valued.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-206">Per altre informazioni, vedere gli argomenti di adschema "[membro](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_member.asp)"e"[Managed By](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_managedby.asp)" in MSDN Library all'indirizzo [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-206">For more information, see the adschema topics "[Member](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_member.asp)" and "[Managed-By](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/default.asp?url=/library/en-us/adschema/adschema/a_managedby.asp)" in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-207">La ricerca viene eseguita sugli oggetti che vengono identificati dal nome distinto specificato nell'attributo dell'oggetto di base.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-207">The search is performed against the objects that are identified by the distinguished name that is specified in the attribute of the base object.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-208">Ad esempio, se l'oggetto di base è un gruppo adschema e <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> è impostato su "member", quindi verrà eseguita la ricerca su tutti gli oggetti che sono membri del gruppo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-208">For example, if the base object is an adschema group class and the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> is set to "member," then the search will be performed against all objects that are members of the group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-209">Per altre informazioni, vedere l'argomento di classe adschema "Gruppo" in MSDN Library all'indirizzo [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-209">For more information, see the adschema "Group" class topic in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-210">Quando la <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> proprietà viene utilizzata, la <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> proprietà deve essere impostata su <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-210">When the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property is used, the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property must be set to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.SearchScope.Base>.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-211">Se il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> è impostata su qualsiasi altro valore, impostare il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> proprietà genererà una <xref:System.ArgumentException>.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-211">If the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchScope%2A> property is set to any other value, setting the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property will throw an <xref:System.ArgumentException>.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-212">Per altre informazioni, vedere l'argomento "Esecuzione di una Query con ambito attributo" in MSDN Library all'indirizzo [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library)).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-212">For more information, see the "Performing an Attribute Scope Query" topic in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library)).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-213">Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato come utilizzare il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> proprietà con l'attributo member per ottenere i membri di un gruppo.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-213">The following example shows how to use the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.AttributeScopeQuery%2A> property with the member attribute to get the members of a group.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-214">Quindi stampa i nomi e cognomi dei membri e i numeri di telefono.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-214">It then prints out the first and last names of the members and their telephone numbers.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
DirectoryEntry group = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=MyGroup, …");  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher(group "(&(objectClass=user)(objectCategory=Person))");  
src.AttributeScopedQuery = "member";  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("sn");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("givenName");  
src.PropertiesToLoad.Add("telephoneNumber");  
foreach(SearchResult res in src.FindAll())  
{  
    Console.WriteLine("…");  
}  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-232">Nell'esempio c# seguente viene illustrato come impostare il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> proprietà <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> , in modo che Dereferenzia gli alias durante la ricerca nei subordinati e l'individuazione degli oggetti di base.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-232">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.DerefAlias%2A> property to <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DereferenceAlias.Always> , so that it dereferences aliases when both searching subordinates and locating base objects.</span></span>  
  
```  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
// Bind to the users container.  
DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("LDAP://CN=users,DC=fabrikam,DC=com");  
// Create a DirectorySearcher object.  
DirectorySearcher mySearcher = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
// Set DerefAlias to Always.  
src.DerefAlias = DerefenceAlias.Always;  
//Use the FindAll method to get search results.  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-242">Nell'esempio seguente viene illustrato come restituire una raccolta di nomi distinti in formato esadecimale.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-242">The following example shows how to return a collection of distinguished names in hexadecimal format.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.ExtendedDN = ExtendedDN.HexString;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-303">Se <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> è un riferimento null (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), il percorso di ricerca è impostato sulla radice del dominio a cui il server è attualmente in uso.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-303">If <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.SearchRoot%2A> is a null reference (`Nothing` in Visual Basic), the search root is set to the root of the domain that your server is currently using.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-304">Esistono diversi modi per eseguire la ricerca nel catalogo globale:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-304">There are several ways to search in the global catalog:</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="0439a-305">Enumerare il catalogo globale e scegliere il primo elemento figlio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-305">Enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="0439a-306">Specificare il nome del server.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-306">Specify the server name.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-307">Utilizzare la funzione DsGetDcName per individuare il catalogo globale.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-307">Use the DsGetDcName function to find the global catalog.</span></span>  <span data-ttu-id="0439a-308">Per altre informazioni sulla funzione DsGetDcName, vedere l'argomento "DsGetDcName" in MSDN Library all'indirizzo [ http://msdn.microsoft.com/library ](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-308">For more information on the DsGetDcName function, see the topic "DsGetDcName" in the MSDN Library at [http://msdn.microsoft.com/library](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library).</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="0439a-309">Recupero di RootDSE del catalogo globale e richiesta di "rootNamingContext".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-309">Get the RootDSE  of the global catalog and ask for "rootNamingContext".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="0439a-310">Usare il catalogo globale, che specifica un percorso di ricerca come se tramite il protocollo LDAP.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-310">Use the global catalog, specifying a search path as if using LDAP.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="0439a-311">Ad esempio, "GC: / / OU =..., DC =..., DC =...".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-311">For example, "GC://OU=..., DC=..., DC=...".</span></span>  
  
-   <span data-ttu-id="0439a-312">Il codice c# seguente viene illustrato come enumerare il catalogo globale e scegliere il primo elemento figlio.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-312">The following C# code shows how to enumerate the global catalog and pick the first child.</span></span>  
  
    ```csharp  
    DirectoryEntry entry = new DirectoryEntry("GC://forestname");  
    IEnumerator ie = entry.Children.GetEnumerator();  
    ie.MoveNext();  
    entry = (DirectoryEntry)ie.Current;  
    DirectorySearcher search = new DirectorySearcher(entry);  
    ```

  
  
## Examples  
  
```csharp  
using System.DirectoryServices;  
...  
DirectorySearcher src = new DirectorySearcher("…");  
src.PropertiesToLoad = new string[] {ntSecurityDescriptor,…};  
src.SecurityMasks = SecurityMasks.Dacl | SecurityMasks.Owner;  
SearchResultCollection res = src.FindAll();  
  
```

  
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="0439a-350">Nell'esempio c# seguente viene illustrato come impostare il <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> proprietà `true`.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="0439a-350">The following C# example shows how to set the <xref:System.DirectoryServices.DirectorySearcher.Tombstone%2A> property to `true`.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
